race.comment: KEEPMEINTHELOPE (4) has put back-to-back wins together to start the campaign and is racing with a lot of confidence this time in work. The penny may have dropped now and rates the testing material. GOLD FEVER (5) is yet to miss a quinella spot in three spins around this circuit and will be ready to peak now third-up from the break. Right in this contest. Former NSW galloper BOTANICA (3) just missed the frame when having the first run for the new stable and will have come on with that run now under the belt. In the mix. COLLEANO (9) gets in light with the claim and can run a race while fresh. FLYING SHELLY (11) next in line with Maloney on board from the inside alley.
